{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 69,
    "name": "سُورَةُ الحَاقَّةِ",
    "englishName": "Al-Haaqqa",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Reality",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 52,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 5324,
        "text": "真实的[如复活日]！",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5325,
        "text": "真实的是什么？",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5326,
        "text": "你怎能知道真实的是什么？",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5327,
        "text": "萨姆德人和阿德人曾否认大难[审判时的敲钟声]。",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5328,
        "text": "至于萨姆德人，已被恐怖的叫喊声所毁灭；",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5329,
        "text": "至于阿德人，已被怒吼的狂风所毁灭。",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5330,
        "text": "他[安拉]曾使狂风向他们连续刮了七夜八天，你看见人们被刮倒在地上[被毁灭]，他们好像空心的椰枣树干一样。",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5331,
        "text": "你看见他们还有遗存的吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5332,
        "text": "法老和在他[法老]之前的人们，以及被颠覆的城市的人民[如鲁特圣人所居城市的人民]曾犯罪。",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5333,
        "text": "他们违抗他们的主的使者，所以，他严厉惩罚了他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5334,
        "text": "[努哈圣人时代]当洪水泛滥时，我让你们[努哈圣人及其追随者]乘坐在[努哈圣人制造的]船中，",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5335,
        "text": "以便我使它成为对你们的一种教诲，以便灵敏的耳[人]能[听见并]理解。",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5336,
        "text": "当号角[第一次]一吹响，",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5337,
        "text": "大地和群山被移开，彼此碰撞一次时，",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5338,
        "text": "在那日，那大事将发生，",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5339,
        "text": "天将破裂。在那日，天是脆弱的[将裂成碎片]。",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5340,
        "text": "天使们将在天的各边。在那日，在他们的上面将有八位天使抬着你的主的宝座[注]。",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5341,
        "text": "在那日，你们将被带出[受审]，你们没有任何秘密可隐瞒。",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5342,
        "text": "至于功过簿递给右手者，他将说：“你们拿我的功过簿去念吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5343,
        "text": "我[在尘世时已]确信我必将遇见我的帐目。”",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5344,
        "text": "他将在愉快的生活中，",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5345,
        "text": "在一个高级乐园中，",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5346,
        "text": "园里的水果伸手可摘。",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5347,
        "text": "[有话声说]：“你们愉快地吃喝吧！因为你们在过去的岁月里[信仰并]行善。”",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5348,
        "text": "至于功过簿递给左手者，他将说：“要是我的功过簿不递给我多好啊！",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5349,
        "text": "要是我不知道我的帐目多好啊！",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5350,
        "text": "要是[在尘世的]死亡能结束我的一生多好啊！",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5351,
        "text": "我的财富对我无益了，",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5352,
        "text": "我的权力从我的掌握中消失了。”",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5353,
        "text": "[有话声说]：“你们抓住他，给他戴上脚镣；",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5354,
        "text": "然后，你们把他扔进烈火中去；",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5355,
        "text": "然后，你们用一根七十臂长的链子拴住他。”",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5356,
        "text": "这是因为他[在尘世时]不信仰伟大的安拉，",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5357,
        "text": "不劝勉人们济贫[注]。",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 567,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5358,
        "text": "因此，今天他在这里没有任何朋友，",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5359,
        "text": "除[伤口流出的]脓汁外，他没有任何食物[可吃]，",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5360,
        "text": "只有罪人才吃那脓汁。",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 500,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5361,
        "text": "我以你们看得见的一切发誓，",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 501,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5362,
        "text": "以你们看不见的一切发誓，",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 501,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5363,
        "text": "这[《古兰经》]确是一位尊贵使者[吉布里勒天使或穆圣转述]的言辞，",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 501,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5364,
        "text": "这不是一位诗人的言辞，但你们很少信仰。",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 501,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5365,
        "text": "这也不是一位占卜者的言辞，但你们很少接受劝告。",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 501,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5366,
        "text": "这[《古兰经》]是从众世界之主降示的。",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 501,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5367,
        "text": "假如他[穆圣]借我[安拉]的名义捏造一些谎言，",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 501,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5368,
        "text": "我必以权力惩治他，",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 501,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5369,
        "text": "然后，我必割断他的主动脉，",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 501,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5370,
        "text": "你们中绝没有人能阻止我惩罚他。",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 501,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5371,
        "text": "这[《古兰经》]确是对敬畏者的教诲。",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 501,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5372,
        "text": "我的确知道你们中谁是否认[《古兰经》]者。",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 501,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5373,
        "text": "[复活日]，这[《古兰经》]确是不信仰者悲痛[后悔]的泉源。",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 501,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5374,
        "text": "这[《古兰经》]确是绝对的真理。",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 501,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5375,
        "text": "所以，你当赞颂你伟大的主的尊名。",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 568,
        "ruku": 501,
        "hizbQuarter": 227,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
